<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>很抱歉，系统出错了，请稍后访问</title>
    <link href="@Url.Content("~/styles/site.css")" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <script src="@Url.Content("~/scripts/kissy/1.2.0/kissy-min.js")" type="text/javascript"></script> 
    <style type="text/css">
        .wrapper{ background-color:#fff;padding:10px;width:600px;margin:0 auto;}
        .wrapper h2{color:#333;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;}
        .wrapper h3{color:#666;}
        .wrapper h3 strong{margin:0 6px;color:#a10000;font-weight:bold;}
        .blank0{clear:both;display:block;font-size:1px;visibility:hidden;height:0;line-height:0;}
        .blank5{clear:both;display:block;font-size:1px;overflow:hidden;height:5px;}
        .blank8{clear:both;display:block;font-size:1px;overflow:hidden;height:8px;}
        .blank10{clear:both;display:block;font-size:1px;overflow:hidden;height:10px;}
        .blank12{clear:both;display:block;font-size:1px;overflow:hidden;height:12px;}
        .blank15{clear:both;display:block;font-size:1px;overflow:hidden;height:15px;}
        .blank20{clear:both;display:block;font-size:1px;overflow:hidden;height:20px;}
        .blank25{clear:both;display:block;font-size:1px;overflow:hidden;height:25px;}
        .btn-back{width:85px;height:26px;margin-left:10px;padding-left:18px;background:url(/images/btn-home-bg.gif) no-repeat;color:#fff;border:0;cursor:pointer;}
        .btn-area span,.btn-area input{line-height:26px;float:left;display:inline;}
        .btn-area span{color:#666;}
    </style>    
    <script type="text/javascript">
        
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
    <span class="blank15"></span><span class="blank15"></span>
    <h2>
        很抱歉，系统出错了，请您耐心等待几分钟，我们的服务很快就能恢复。</h2>
    <span class="blank8"></span>
    <h3>
        将在<strong id="sec">10</strong>秒后自动转入首页。</h3>
    <span class="blank20"></span>
    <div class="btn-area">
        <span>您也可以：</span><input type="button" value="返回首页" class="btn-back" onclick="window.location.href='/'" />
    </div>
</div>
  <script type="text/javascript">
      KISSY.ready(function (S) {
          var DOM = S.DOM, $ = S.all;
          function lazyBackHome() {
              var sec = $("#sec").text();
              $("#sec").text(--sec);
              if (sec > 0)
                  setTimeout(arguments.callee, 1000);
              else
                  window.location.href = "/";
          }
          lazyBackHome();
      });
   </script>
</body>
</html>